Happy Holidays, everyone!

The festive spirit is in the air, as well as in our latest update! And we’re not talking just about the pretty app icon either:
– A shiny new box full of Holidays-themed missions to fill your wallet with the jolly spirit of Capitalism ;)
– A bunch of Holiday-themed modifiers to your Happiness and Health
– A freshly decorated Christmas tree on the main screen. And it’s not a mere decoration either! Tap on it to find a present of a Holiday-themed story, and be sure to check for a push notification to access it as soon as possible!

Happy Holidays, and see you soon!

Greetings, everyone!
We’re back from the holiday vacations with an update to share with all of you:
– Thrown out the withering Christmas tree and put the decorations and garlands back into their box until the next holiday season.
– Santa Claus had promptly disappeared once the background Christmas magic radiation had reached its critical lows.
– Changed some of the in-game events according to your feedback to make them even more fun.
– Fixed a few known technical problems and made the app a bit more stable.
